==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*ἔκστασις / ekstasis / ek'-stas-is

===Etymology===
From [[ἐξίστημι]] {{GG|1839}}; 

===Noun===
'''ἔκστασις'''

# a displacement of the mind, that is, [[bewilderment]], “[[ecstasy]]”: - + be amazed, [[amazement]], [[astonishment]], [[trance]].

